value: Breeds on the Commander Islands, Kamchatka and the Kurile Islands; possibly breeds on some of the Aleutians east to Unalaska. Chiefly resident, but recorded in winter to northern Japan.
refer: Peter's Checklist of the Birds of the World

value: Mostly pelagic; nests in crevices in talus slopes, among boulders along beaches, and on lava flows on high slopes.

subcat_descr: Bill length (sex unknown) - Nares to tip
